<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbe07b534-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7382f"><num value="7382f">§ 7382f.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idbe07b535-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7382f/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated for the Program $700,000 for fiscal year 1995, and such sums as may be necessary for each of the four succeeding fiscal years.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idbe07b536-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7382f/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> WERC program</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated for the WERC program under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s7382e">section 7382e of this title</ref> such sums as may be necessary for fiscal year 1995 and each of the four succeeding fiscal years.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idbe07b537-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/382/tV/s518">Pub. L. 103–382, title V, § 518</ref>, <date date="1994-10-20">Oct. 20, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/4044">108 Stat. 4044</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
